Terraform modules:

Module is like a container logically related and can be used together

General Structure of a modules folder

    Ex: Modules\<Componet nname>: main.tf 
                                  output.tf
                                  Readme.md 
                                  variables.tf 

    Values of ouput from modul1 can be used by Module2

    terraform --auto-aprove


You can remove specific resource by commenting that code out 
After commenting you code when you check terraform plan
it will treat commented code as :: I need to remove this :: 